    "body": {
      "input": "Content: When the script finishes, a success or failure email will be sent to the emails associated with the system.\n\nPlease refer to the SSH Guide for SSH connection information.\n\nAPI scripts\nupdate.sh\nUpdate the Pega Platform to a specific version and then check to make sure the Designer Studio is up and accessible after the update.\n\nParameters\n--PlatformVersion\nDesired Pega platform version. Must adhere to the Pega Labs naming convention:\n\nmajor.minor.patch-suffix\n\nwhere suffix is one of: GA, B[n], HEAD[n], DEV[n], or latest.\n\nFor example: 8.7.0-GA, 8.24.0-DEV1234, 8.23.2-HEAD1234, 8.24.0-latest.\n\nExamples\n./update.sh --PlatformVersion 8.8.4-GA\n./update.sh --PlatformVersion 8.24.0-latest\n./update.sh --PlatformVersion latest\ninstall.sh\nReinstalls the Pega Platform with a specific version and then check to make sure the Designer Studio is up and accessible after the install.\n\nParameters\n--PlatformVersion same as with update.\n\n--DisableSecureInstall [true|<no input>]"
    }
  },
